channel.title: Google Chrome Censor?
channel.description:
Anyone know how to turn this shit off and why it's even happening? It's PayPal for crying out loud. I can't access the site at all, there's not even a "proceed anyway" link.
[IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/14uxo41.png[/img]
And my computer's on a fresh install so I know I'm not infected, I haven't downloaded anything.

item.title: Google Chrome Censor?
item.dc:creator: @ggallin ggallin
item.description:
@ggallin wrote:

Carter_:

You mention DNS settings… I had actually just changed my DNS settings because I was having trouble connecting to the internet. They were set to 8.8.8.8 and 8.8.4.4, which is apparently Google’s server if what the source said was true?

yeah it is.
